    <string name="hi">HI!</string>
    <string name="m1_tutorial">It seems it\'s your first time using Language Database</string>
    <string name=  "tutorial_m3">This is a basic language app, where you can store and practice with your own vocabulary by creating groups of words, adding info and testing it. \n \n let\'s get started!!</string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m4">In order to make progress, you will have to maintain an equilibrium between adding words and making tests. </string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m5">Each word can have two states: acquired or not acquired.</string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m6">Whenever you correctly translate a word several times in different days,its status will change to "acquired"</string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m7">You will be able to perform tests by clicking the "T" option in the superior right part of the menu.</string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m8">Overall, you can not have more than 120 words in the "not acquired" form, and hence, you will have to simultaneously
        keep doing tests and adding words.</string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m9">When adding a new word, you wil have to fill out the fields "word" and "translation". You will
    also have the option to provide a definition and an example. All this information can be edited later on. </string>
    <string name = "tutorial_m10">Enjoy the learning process!!</string>
